column3: \n◦ Brought to live solution for managing PII data and made the flow almost automate with minimal\nengineer involvement

column6: \n◦ Investigate data issues, the root causes and possible consequences, provide the appropriate\nsolution
column8: \n◦ Fix and resolve alerts for the infrastructure (pager duty, sensu)
column9:
